In On-Track Beginning Reading K-1 software, your child will get to know a frog that jogs and some very smart hens in two delightful stories that make reading fun. Simple sentences, repeated and rhyming words, audio guidance and picture clues ensure reading success. Children will explore a handy dictionary as they reference words and pictures found in the stories. Plus, Create-a-Story lets children discover creative writing and art as they write and illustrate their own stories. Each storybook is included for off-screen reading.
